@gechiang @Praveen-Brcm looks like the whole function does not work at all because it consists of 2 cases: [port isolation group](https://github.com/novikauanton/sonic-swss/blob/4664ead03c220bb91ef97746f3dd97232be46828/mclagsyncd/mclaglink.cpp#L192) and [ACL isolation](https://github.com/novikauanton/sonic-swss/blob/4664ead03c220bb91ef97746f3dd97232be46828/mclagsyncd/mclaglink.cpp#L273).
ACL isolation does not work due to this issue. 
Port isolation does not work because it use [env `platform` to check its condition](https://github.com/novikauanton/sonic-swss/blob/4664ead03c220bb91ef97746f3dd97232be46828/mclagsyncd/mclaglink.cpp#L191) and `mclagsyncd` work inside `iccpd` container and [`iccpd` container does not set `platform` env](https://github.com/Azure/sonic-buildimage/pull/8945) so code in port isolation branch will never be executed.

